	<h1 class="title">水果姐代言H&amp;M，为什么她不担心失去高端品牌？</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/399912/small/399912.JPG?1452046699" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">张田小 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-07-19 08:08:00 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/12296/medium/12296.jpg?1437130784" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


